{"tid":2170214,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【上周做手術】TWICE定延新相報平安 意外撞樣金世正","createTime":"2020-08-23T06:16:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-23T16:04:11.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c51fdfa720b70a594d425d244b6a7593293759aa","tid":2170214,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T06:16:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/GNc4aM0HHYVN9Us9jr3i37ysV7o=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2UMYHJ5ZMNAG5CVK6NUHKOBRMA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FGNc4aM0HHYVN9Us9jr3i37ysV7o%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2UMYHJ5ZMNAG5CVK6NUHKOBRMA.jpg&h=a6d1f635&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTWICE定延晒新相，意外跟女團gu9udan成員金世正撞樣<br />\n<br />\n韓國女團TWICE自出道後就十分忙碌，在高強度的活動下，不時爆出成員身體亮紅燈的消息，令fans十分擔心。<br />\n<br />\n23歲成員定延上周因為頸椎間盤突出而做了手術，更缺席《Soribada最佳音樂大獎》，專心休養，她昨晚透過IG公開了自拍照，只見她化了妝、對着鏡頭甜笑，表現出平時開朗一面，獲不少fans留言叫她要快點康復，不過就有網民指，未知是妝容還是角度問題，定延似乎跟女團gu9udan成員金世正撞樣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/i8gA_eJ6Y6P6gNYREUYJW-1WtO0=/802x1178/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TMYEPBQ57VBQXNAKPIJN6KCEM4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fi8gA_eJ6Y6P6gNYREUYJW-1WtO0%3D%2F802x1178%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTMYEPBQ57VBQXNAKPIJN6KCEM4.jpg&h=cbab593e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/aA337kLKeXHqGLgCDOQUjr9V-mo=/802x802/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/M2INE5UVANGSDORE74THZLLGDY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FaA337kLKeXHqGLgCDOQUjr9V-mo%3D%2F802x802%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FM2INE5UVANGSDORE74THZLLGDY.jpg&h=57899f22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/kRm0GpBl9gaPv_KJNV2XVYqJlWc=/802x1215/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2JQQP3TDGBGN7OFQB5F7KZANGI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FkRm0GpBl9gaPv_KJNV2XVYqJlWc%3D%2F802x1215%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2JQQP3TDGBGN7OFQB5F7KZANGI.jpg&h=d6d11fee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而組合的台灣成員周子瑜，近日為服裝品牌拍攝新相時，就收起甜美笑容變身為冰山美人，展現出不同魅力，同樣獲fans大讚。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200823/7ASEWYZIFJAVBOHABA52HQLYCQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200823%2F7ASEWYZIFJAVBOHABA52HQLYCQ%2F&d=MZ%2BcikgbnzcLbT%2Fpq7%2BWTHGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=37973020\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200823%2F7ASEWYZIFJAVBOHABA52HQLYCQ%2F&h=dd9c92e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200823/7ASEWYZIFJAVBOHABA52HQLYCQ/</a>"},{"pid":"ca49353ffe7d1586c4b939d11ee1bf2135c07335","tid":2170214,"uid":74065,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T06:16:40.000Z","msg":"牙CLEAN&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;TB定"},{"pid":"299950bf863f02afde485733d077514dd9f611b7","tid":2170214,"uid":33359,"like":4,"dislike":18,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T06:19:42.000Z","msg":"唔識邊位金世正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定延正好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc378912d7cda4d5267ffe12369e79385423354e","tid":2170214,"uid":261849,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-0